Throughout Yusuke's journey, he is usually joined by; his arch-rival, and local bully, Kuwabara Kazuma. He is also joined by two demons named Hiei and Kurama, whom are ex-convicts of the afterlife that managed to escape from Koenma.<br><br>
This group of unlikely allies goes on to participate and struggle in battles that have outcomes that determine the fate of humanity!<br><br>
